    • Constructor Detail

      • RadarPlace

        public RadarPlace(java.lang.String id,
                  java.lang.String facebookId,
                  java.lang.String facebookPlaceId,
                  java.lang.String name,
                  java.lang.String[] categories,
                  RadarChain chain,
                  Coordinate location,
                  java.lang.String group,
                  org.json.JSONObject metadata)

        Represents a place. For more information about Places, https://radar.io/documentation/places.

        Parameters:
        id - The Radar ID of the place.
        facebookId - The Facebook page ID of the place, if known.
        facebookPlaceId - The Facebook place ID of the place, if known.
        name - The name of the place.
        categories - The categories of the place. For a full list of categories, see https://radar.io/documentation/places/categories.
        chain - The chain of the place, if known. May be null for places without a chain. For a full list of chains, see https://radar.io/documentation/places/chains.
        location - The location of the place.
        group - The group for the place, if any. For a full list of groups, see https://radar.io/documentation/places/groups.
        metadata - The metadata for the place, if part of a group. For details of metadata fields see https://radar.io/documentation/places/groups.
        See Also:
        https://radar.io/documentation/places
